trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:Accessibility.IAccPropServices" /> interface and all of its exposed members are part of a managed wrapper for the Component Object Model (COM) <see langword="IAccPropServices" /> interface.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:Accessibility.IAccPropServices" /> 接口及其公开的所有成员都属于组件对象模型 (COM) <see langword="IAccPropServices" /> 接口的托管包装的一部分。

trans-unit.source: Identifies the accessible element that is to be annotated.
trans-unit.target: 标识要批注的可访问元素。

trans-unit.source: Specifies the length of the string identified by the <c>pIDString</c> parameter.
trans-unit.target: 指定由 <c>pIDString</c> 参数标识的字符串的长度。

trans-unit.source: Specifies the property of the accessible element to be annotated.
trans-unit.target: 指定要批注的可访问元素的属性。

trans-unit.source: Specifies a new value for the property.
trans-unit.target: 为属性指定一个新值。
